Kestrel













Kestrel is an independent investment manager dedicated to building the wealth of our institutional and private clients over the long term.
We manage a range of specialist funds and services that are innovative and validated by their successful performance. Every Kestrel product has a precise focus and its own unique strategy, but all share a consistent approach: our funds are run according to disciplined investment principles by experienced fund managers, who are absolutely focused on protecting and growing wealth over the long term.









